Package: ggwordcloud
Type: Package
Title: A wordcloud geom for ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Erwan", "Le Pennec", email = "lepennec@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kamil", "Slowikowski", email = "kslowikowski@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Erwan Le Pennec <lepennec@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a wordcloud text geom for ggplot2. Texts are placed so that they do not overlap as in ggrepel.
    The algorithm used is a variation around the one of wordcloud2.js.
